lead_paragraph: Garbine Muguruza had the rare experience of winning her final match of the season without lifting a trophy, an almost fitting end to a year of frustration for the Spaniard who claimed her first grand slam but had little else to celebrate.

headline.print_headline: Muguruza Finds Little Comfort in Bittersweet Victory
